Class GymOwner

java.lang.Object
com.flipfit.bean.User
com.flipfit.bean.GymOwner
public class GymOwner extends User
Represents a gym owner in the FlipFit system. Extends the base User class with owner-specific professional and tax details.
Author:
team IOTA
